rmd-typography-font-weights.name: rmd-typography-font-weights
rmd-typography-font-weights.value:
(
  thin: 100,
  light: 300,
  regular: 400,
  medium: 500,
  bold: 700,
  semi-bold: 800,
  black: 900, // sass-lint:disable-line no-color-keywords
)

rmd-typography-google-font-weight-suffix.name: rmd-typography-google-font-weight-suffixes
rmd-typography-google-font-weight-suffix.value:
(
  thin: '-Thin',
  light: '-Light',
  regular: '-Regular',
  medium: '-Medium',
  bold: '-Bold',
  semi-bold: '-SemiBold',
  black: '-Black', // sass-lint:disable-line no-color-keywords
)

rmd-typography-base.name: rmd-typography-base
rmd-typography-base.value:
(
  font-family: $rmd-typography-font-family,
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale, // sass-lint:disable-line no-vendor-prefixes
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased, // sass-lint:disable-line no-vendor-prefixes
)

rmd-theme-text-colors.name: rmd-theme-text-colors
rmd-theme-text-colors.value:
(
  dark: (
    primary: rgba($rmd-black-base, .87),
    secondary: rgba($rmd-black-base, .54),
    hint: rgba($rmd-black-base, .34),
    disabled: rgba($rmd-black-base, .38),
    icon: rgba($rmd-black-base, .54),
  ),
  light: (
    primary: $rmd-white-base,
    secondary: rgba($rmd-white-base, .7),
    hint: rgba($rmd-white-base, .5),
    disabled: rgba($rmd-white-base, .5),
    icon: rgba($rmd-white-base, .7),
  ),
)
